org.easetech.easytest.internal

Class EasyAssignments

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.easetech.easytest.internal.EasyAssignments

  • public class EasyAssignments
extends Object
    An internal util class for working with the parameters of a test method. This class provides EasyTest the facility to identify the method arguments, identify the DataSupplier associated with the Test Framework and more.
    Author:
    Anuj Kumar
